# UI/Component Guidelines

- Use Shadcn UI and Radix components for UI
- Tailwind CSS for mobile-first, responsive design
- Implement error and loading states for all data fetching
- Use descriptive variable names (e.g., isLoading, hasError)
- Avoid magic numbers; use named constants
- Include emoji console logs for debugging
- Use functional programming and avoid classes
- Follow modular design for maintainability
